<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<%- include('../layout', { seo, baseUrl }) %>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box}body{margin:0;font-family:'Manrope',sans-serif;background:#0a0d12;color:#f5f7fb;line-height:1.7}a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit}.wrap{width:min(980px,calc(100% - 32px));margin:0 auto}.top{padding:24px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}.top-in{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px}.brand{font-size:22px;font-weight:800}.brand span{color:#d7b35d}.links{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;color:#9ea8bb}.hero{padding:64px 0 24px}.hero h1{font-size:clamp(36px,7vw,62px);line-height:1.04;margin:0 0 12px}.hero p{max-width:760px;color:#b2bccf}.section{padding:18px 0 42px}.card{background:#121722;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:24px;padding:28px;margin-top:18px}.card h2{margin:0 0 12px;font-size:28px}.card h3{margin:22px 0 8px;font-size:19px}.card p,.card li{color:#d9e1ef}.card ul{padding-left:20px}.muted{color:#9ea8bb}.footer{padding:30px 0 40px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}.footer-links{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;color:#9ea8bb}@media (max-width:720px){.top-in{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="top">
  <div class="wrap top-in">
    <a href="/" class="brand">VibeNote<span>.studio</span></a>
    <nav class="links" aria-label="Site links">
      <a href="/docs">Docs</a>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
      <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
      <a href="/cookies">Cookies</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>
<main>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="muted">Legal</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>This policy explains what information VibeNote collects to help agencies generate, edit, and deploy client websites.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Data we collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Account information such as agency name, email, login details, and billing status.</li>
          <li>Client brief data including business information, services, branding, assets, contact details, and SEO inputs.</li>
          <li>Generated websites, deployment metadata, and project activity needed to operate the platform.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>How we use data</h3>
        <p>We use submitted information to authenticate accounts, generate websites, support editing workflows, manage deployments, and improve platform reliability.</p>
        <h3>Third-party services</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Supabase for authentication and database operations.</li>
          <li>Anthropic AI for website generation.</li>
          <li>Cloudflare for static hosting workflows.</li>
          <li>Razorpay for payments and subscription processing.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Storage and retention</h2>
        <p>Project data, generated website files, and account details may be stored while your account is active and for a reasonable period afterward to support support requests, billing, and legal compliance.</p>
        <h3>Your responsibilities</h3>
        <p>Agencies should only submit client information and assets they are authorized to use. Sensitive information should not be included unless necessary for the website project.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="wrap top-in">
    <div class="muted">Questions about privacy can be sent to your VibeNote support contact.</div>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="/docs">Docs</a>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
      <a href="/cookies">Cookie Policy</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
